nodes.title: Definitions
widgets_values:
This node sets the image's resolution in Width and Height.

NOTE: For SDXL, it is recommended to use trained values listed below:
 - 1024 x 1024
 - 1152 x 896
 - 896  x 1152
 - 1216 x 832
 - 832  x 1216
 - 1344 x 768
 - 768  x 1344
 - 1536 x 640
 - 640  x 1536
